/**
 * shadcn/ui components directory
 *
 * Components added via `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` will be placed here.
 * Each component is fully customizable since the code is owned by the project.
 *
 * Example:
 *   npx shadcn@latest add button
 *   npx shadcn@latest add dialog
 *   npx shadcn@latest add dropdown-menu
 */
